iv><\/div><div class=\"et_pb_column_3 et_pb_column et_flex_column et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et_flex_column_24_24 et_flex_column_24_24_tablet et_flex_column_24_24_phone\"><div class=\"et_pb_heading_2 et_pb_heading et_pb_module et_flex_module\"><div class=\"et_pb_heading_container\"><h1 class=\"et_pb_module_header\">Saskatchewan Coverage Areas<\/h1><\/div><\/div><div class=\"et_pb_image_2 et_pb_image et_pb_module et_flex_module\"><span class=\"et_pb_image_wrap\"><img data-dominant-color=\"5d684e\" data-has-transparency=\"false\" style=\"--dominant-color: #5d684e;\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/IDM-Coverage-jpg.webp\" title=\"Saskatchewan IDM Coverage\" width=\"750\" height=\"750\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/IDM-Coverage-jpg.webp 750w, https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/IDM-Coverage-480x480.webp 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 750px, 100vw\" class=\"wp-image-211200 not-transparent\" \/><\/span><\/div><div class=\"et_pb_text_3 et_pb_text et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_module et_flex_module\"><div class=\"et_pb_text_inner\"><p><strong>High-resolution LiDAR provides detailed contour and IDM data in shaded areas, while other regions are covered by lower-accuracy satellite-based terrain modeling.<\/strong><\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"et_pb_column_4 et_pb_column et_flex_column et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et_flex_column_24_24 et_flex_column_24_24_tablet et_flex_column_24_24_phone\"><div class=\"et_pb_heading_3 et_pb_heading et_pb_module et_flex_module\"><div class=\"et_pb_heading_container\"><h1 class=\"et_pb_module_header\">Alberta Coverage Areas<\/h1><\/div><\/div><div class=\"et_pb_image_3 et_pb_image et_pb_module et_flex_module\"><span class=\"et_pb_image_wrap\"><img data-dominant-color=\"556554\" data-has-transparency=\"false\" style=\"--dominant-colo