\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/IDM2.jpg\" title=\"IDM2\" width=\"609\" height=\"615\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/IDM2.jpg 609w, https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/IDM2-480x485.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 609px, 100vw\" class=\"wp-image-209401\" \/><\/span><\/div><div class=\"et_pb_text_11 et_pb_text et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_module et_flex_module preset--module--divi-text--7321ddd3-b161-4357-8b61-e6229e3c93ce\"><div class=\"et_pb_text_inner\"><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>Use them to Understand Water Movement and Guide Drain Placements for Efficient Water Management<\/span><\/h3>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"et_pb_column_13 et_pb_column et-last-child et_flex_column et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et_flex_column_24_24 et_flex_column_24_24_tablet et_flex_column_24_24_phone\"><div class=\"et_pb_image_9 et_pb_image et_pb_module et_flex_module\"><span class=\"et_pb_image_wrap\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/DA_Layer.jpg\" title=\"DA_Layer\" width=\"658\" height=\"637\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/DA_Layer.jpg 658w, https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/DA_Layer-480x465.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 658px, 100vw\" class=\"wp-image-209402\" \/><\/span><\/div><div class=\"et_pb_text_12 et_pb_text et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_module et_flex_module preset--module--divi-text--7321ddd3-b161-4357-8b61-e6229e3c93ce\"><div class=\"et_pb_text_inner\"><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>NEW: Download IDM and field elevation contour layers directrly into the Ditch Assist App and access in the field<\/span><\/h3>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"et_pb_row_6 et_pb_row et_flex_row\"><div class=\"et_pb_column_14 et_pb_column et-last-child et_flex_column et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et_flex_column_24_24 et_flex_column_24_24_tablet et_flex_column_24_24_phone\"><div class=\"et_pb_heading_7 et_pb_heading et_pb_module et_flex_module\"><div class=\"et_pb_heading_container\"><h3 class=\"et_pb_module_header\">When you sign-up we'll send you detailed instructions to download IDM and Contour Maps right into your Ditch Assist App, as well as a link to setup your Portal login access<\/h3><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"et_pb_section_2 et_pb_section et_section_regular et_flex_section\"><div class=\"et_pb_row_7 et_pb_row et_flex_row\"><div class=\"et_pb_column_15 et_pb_column et_flex_column et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et_flex_column_24_24 et_flex_column_24_24_tablet et_flex_column_24_24_phone\"><div class=\"et_pb_image_10 et_pb_image et_pb_module et_flex_module\"><span class=\"et_pb_image_wrap\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/How-To-Create-Value-For-Online-Audience-427x1024.jpg\" title=\"How To Create Value For Online Audience\" width=\"427\" height=\"1024\" class=\"wp-image-209432\" \/><\/span><\/div><\/div><div class=\"et_pb_column_16 et_pb_column et-last-child et_flex_column et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et_flex_column_24_24 et_flex_column_24_24_tablet et_flex_column_24_24_phone\"><div class=\"et_pb_text_13 et_pb_text et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_module et_flex_module preset--module--divi-text--0fde7e48-ea73-4200-8a4a-a5e4b9fa5065\"><div class=\"et_pb_text_inner\"><h4>COMBINING TECHNOLOGY WITH INSIGHT<\/h4>\n<\/div><\/div><div class=\"et_pb_text_14 et_pb_text et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_module et_flex_module preset--module--divi-text--5c12ac9f-ce18-4be0-9b45-2e257c1c222a\"><div class=\"et_pb_text_inner\"><h2>Use Ditch Assist with Ideal Drainage and Contour Mapping for Ultimate Results<\/h2>\n<\/div><\/div><div class=\"et_pb_text_15 et_pb_text et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_module et_flex_module preset--module--divi-text--768a51a2-8b3b-49d9-9c45-80abc614d131\"><div class=\"et_pb_text_inner\"><p data-sourcepos=\"3:1-3:391\"><strong>Struggling to determine where to place your drains or unsure if one end of your field is higher than the other?<\/strong> Ditch Assist and Ideal Drainage Mapping make it easy. Our advanced drainage and contour mapping provide crucial insights into water flow across your fields\u2014far beyond what you can see with the naked eye. With the Portal, you can view, print, and create custom sketches, plus download IDM and contour layers directly into your Ditch Assist app. Use this data to guide your drainage work with greater precision, leading to better results and less wasted effort.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"et_pb_row_8 et_pb_row et_flex_row\"><div class=\"et_pb_column_17 et_pb_column et_flex_column et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et_flex_column_24_24 et_flex_column_24_24_tablet et_flex_column_24_24_phone\"><div class=\"et_pb_text_16 et_pb_text et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_module et_flex_module preset--module--divi-text--0fde7e48-ea73-4200-8a4a-a5e4b9fa5065\"><div class=\"et_pb_text_inner\"><h4>Complementary Access for Ditch Assist Owners<\/h4>\n<\/div><\/div><div class=\"et_pb_text_17 et_pb_text et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_module et_flex_module preset--module--divi-text--5c12ac9f-ce18-4be0-9b45-2e257c1c222a\"><div class=\"et_pb_text_inner\"><h2>Ditch Assist Owners Get Complementary Access\u00a0 to One Available Region<\/h2>\n<\/div><\/div><div class=\"et_pb_text_18 et_pb_text et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_module et_flex_module preset--module--divi-text--768a51a2-8b3b-49d9-9c45-80abc614d131\"><div class=\"et_pb_text_inner\"><p>As a valued <strong>Ditch Assist System Owner<\/strong>, you get complimentary access to your region-specific on-demand Elevation and Drainage Mapping Portal, plus credentials to access and download the layers right in the Ditch Assist App.\u00a0<\/p>\n<p>This exceptional offer is available exclusively to Ditch Assist Owners.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"et_pb_column_18 et_pb_column et-last-child et_flex_column et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et_flex_column_24_24 et_flex_column_24_24_tablet et_flex_column_24_24_phone\"><div class=\"et_pb_image_11 et_pb_image et_pb_module et_flex_module\"><span class=\"et_pb_image_wrap\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/DA_Controller_500x500.png\" title=\"Ditch Assist Control Module\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/DA_Controller_500x500.png 600w, https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/DA_Controller_500x500-480x480.png 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 600px, 100vw\" class=\"wp-image-208481\" \/><\/span><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"et_pb_row_9 et_pb_row et_flex_row\"><div class=\"et_pb_column_19 et_pb_column et-last-child et_flex_column et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et_flex_column_24_24 et_flex_column_24_24_tablet et_flex_column_24_24_phone\"><div class=\"et_pb_heading_8 et_pb_heading et_pb_module et_flex_module\"><div class=\"et_pb_heading_container\"><h1 class=\"et_pb_module_header\">Sign Up for Complimentary Access to Ideal Drainage Maps Here<\/h1><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"et_pb_row_10 et_pb_row et_flex_row\" id=\"idm-signup\"><div class=\"et_pb_column_20 et_pb_column et-last-child et_flex_column et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et_flex_column_24_24 et_flex_column_24_24_tablet et_flex_column_24_24_phone\"><div class=\"et_pb_text_19 et_pb_text et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_module et_flex_module\"><div class=\"et_pb_text_inner\"><div class=\"wpforms-container wpforms-container-full\" id=\"wpforms-209409\"><form id=\"wpforms-form-209409\" class=\"wpforms-validate wpforms-form wpforms-ajax-form\" data-formid=\"209409\" method=\"post\" enctype=\"multipart\/form-data\" action=\"\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/209377\" data-token=\"a9cb7db9c7d5918e4a7ca68340efcbcb\" data-token-time=\"1775251454\"><noscript class=\"wpforms-error-noscript\">Please enable JavaScript in your browser to complete this form.<\/noscript><div class=\"wpforms-field-container\"><div id=\"wpforms-209409-field_12-container\" class=\"wpforms-field wpforms-field-text\" data-field-id=\"12\"><label class=\"wpforms-field-label\" for=\"wpforms-209409-field_12\">Serial Number of Ditch Assist Control Module <span class=\"wpforms-required-label\">*<\/span><\/label><input type=\"text\" id=\"wpforms-209409-field_12\" class=\"wpforms-field-medium wpforms-field-required\" name=\"wpforms[fields][12]\" required><div class=\"wpforms-field-description\">Located on sticker on back of module, begins with JCA-<\/div><\/div><div id=\"wpforms-209409-field_3-container\" class=\"wpforms-field wpforms-field-text\" data-field-id=\"3\"><label class=\"wpforms-field-label\" for=\"wpforms-209409-field_3\">Purchase Date <span class=\"wpforms-required-label\">*<\/span><\/label><input type=\"text\" id=\"wpforms-209409-field_3\" class=\"wpforms-field-medium wpforms-field-required\" name=\"wpforms[fields][3]\" required><div class=\"wpforms-field-description\">Approximate is fine<\/div><\/div><div id=\"wpforms-209409-field_4-container\" class=\"wpforms-field wpforms-field-text\" data-field-id=\"4\"><label class=\"wpforms-field-label\" for=\"wpforms-209409-field_4\">Purchased From <span class=\"wpforms-required-label\">*<\/span><\/label><input type=\"text\" id=\"wpforms-209409-field_4\" class=\"wpforms-field-medium wpforms-field-required\" name=\"wpforms[fields][4]\" required><div class=\"wpforms-field-description\">Dealer Name, Location<\/div><\/div><div id=\"wpforms-209409-field_8-container\" class=\"wpforms-field wpforms-field-name\" data-field-id=\"8\"><label class=\"wpforms-field-label\">Your Name <span class=\"wpforms-required-label\">*<\/span><\/label><div class=\"wpforms-field-row wpforms-field-medium\"><div class=\"wpforms-field-row-block wpforms-first wpforms-one-half\"><input type=\"text\" id=\"wpforms-209409-field_8\" class=\"wpforms-field-name-first wpforms-field-required\" name=\"wpforms[fields][8][first]\" required><label for=\"wpforms-209409-field_8\" class=\"wpforms-field-sublabel after\">First<\/label><\/div><div class=\"wpforms-field-row-block wpforms-one-half\"><input type=\"text\" id=\"wpforms-209409-field_8-last\" class=\"wpforms-field-name-last wpforms-field-required\" name=\"wpforms[fields][8][last]\" required><label for=\"wpforms-209409-field_8-last\" class=\"wpforms-field-sublabel after\">Last<\/label><\/div><\/div><\/div><div id=\"wpforms-209409-field_7-container\" class=\"wpforms-field wpforms-field-email\" data-field-id=\"7\"><label class=\"wpforms-field-label\">Email <span class=\"wpforms-required-label\">*<\/span><\/label><div class=\"wpforms-field-row wpforms-field-medium\"><div class=\"wpforms-field-row-block wpforms-one-half wpforms-first\"><input type=\"email\" id=\"wpforms-209409-field_7\" class=\"wpforms-field-required wpforms-field-email-primary\" name=\"wpforms[fields][7][primary]\" spellcheck=\"false\" required><label for=\"wpforms-209409-field_7\" class=\"wpforms-field-sublabel after\">Email<\/label><\/div><div class=\"wpforms-field-row-block wpforms-one-half\"><input type=\"email\" id=\"wpforms-209409-field_7-secondary\" class=\"wpforms-field-email-secondary wpforms-field-required\" data-rule-confirm=\"#wpforms-209409-field_7\" name=\"wpforms[fields][7][secondary]\" spellcheck=\"false\" required><label for=\"wpforms-209409-field_7-secondary\" class=\"wpforms-field-sublabel after\">Confirm Email<\/label><\/div><\/div><div class=\"wpforms-field-description\">IMPORTANT: Check your email (including Bulk and Spam folders) for a message from 'The Mango Team' with instructions on how to activate your account access. Please allow 2 business days while we process your application before contacting us if you don't receive an email<\/div><\/div><div id=\"wpforms-209409-field_16-container\" class=\"wpforms-field wpforms-field-text\" data-field-id=\"16\"><label class=\"wpforms-field-label\" for=\"wpforms-209409-field_16\">Location <span class=\"wpforms-required-label\">*<\/span><\/label><input type=\"text\" id=\"wpforms-209409-field_16\" class=\"wpforms-field-medium wpforms-field-required\" name=\"wpforms[fields][16]\" required><div class=\"wpforms-field-description\">Nearest major Town or City & Province\/State<\/div><\/div><div id=\"wpforms-209409-field_15-container\" class=\"wpforms-field wpforms-field-text\" data-field-id=\"15\"><label class=\"wpforms-field-label\" for=\"wpforms-209409-field_15\">Phone<\/label><input type=\"text\" id=\"wpforms-209409-field_15\" class=\"wpforms-field-medium\" name=\"wpforms[fields][15]\" ><div class=\"wpforms-field-description\">Optional<\/div><\/div><div id=\"wpforms-209409-field_14-container\" class=\"wpforms-field wpforms-field-textarea\" data-field-id=\"14\"><label class=\"wpforms-field-label\" for=\"wpforms-209409-field_14\">Mailing Address<\/label><textarea id=\"wpforms-209409-field_14\" class=\"wpforms-field-medium\" name=\"wpforms[fields][14]\" ><\/textarea><div class=\"wpforms-field-description\">Optional<\/div><\/div><div id=\"wpforms-209409-field_17-container\" class=\"wpforms-field wpforms-field-checkbox\" data-field-id=\"17\"><label class=\"wpforms-field-label\">Ideal Drainage Map Region(s) Requested <span class=\"wpforms-required-label\">*<\/span><\/label><ul id=\"wpforms-209409-field_17\" class=\"wpforms-field-required\"><li class=\"choice-1 depth-1\"><input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"wpforms-209409-field_17_1\" name=\"wpforms[fields][17][]\" value=\"Manitoba\" required ><label class=\"wpforms-field-label-inline\" for=\"wpforms-209409-field_17_1\">Manitoba<\/label><\/li><li class=\"choice-2 depth-1\"><input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"wpforms-209409-field_17_2\" name=\"wpforms[fields][17][]\" value=\"Saskatchewan\" required ><label class=\"wpforms-field-label-inline\" for=\"wpforms-209409-field_17_2\">Saskatchewan<\/label><\/li><li class=\"choice-3 depth-1\"><input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"wpforms-209409-field_17_3\" name=\"wpforms[fields][17][]\" value=\"Alberta\" required ><label class=\"wpforms-field-label-inline\" for=\"wpforms-209409-field_17_3\">Alberta<\/label><\/li><li class=\"choice-4 depth-1\"><input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"wpforms-209409-field_17_4\" name=\"wpforms[fields][17][]\" value=\"North Dakota\" required ><label class=\"wpforms-field-label-inline\" for=\"wpforms-209409-field_17_4\">North Dakota<\/label><\/li><li class=\"choice-6 depth-1\"><input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"wpforms-209409-field_17_6\" name=\"wpforms[fields][17][]\" value=\"Minnesota\" required ><label class=\"wpforms-field-label-inline\" for=\"wpforms-209409-field_17_6\">Minnesota<\/label><\/li><li class=\"choice-5 depth-1\"><input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"wpforms-209409-field_17_5\" name=\"wpforms[fields][17][]\" value=\"Iowa\" required ><label class=\"wpforms-field-label-inline\" for=\"wpforms-209409-field_17_5\">Iowa<\/label><\/li><\/ul><div class=\"wpforms-field-description\">Verified owners of Ditch Assist receive free access to one available Ideal Drainage Map Portal. If you farm across borders you may select two portals and we will verify with your dealer before granting access.<\/div><\/div><div id=\"wpforms-209409-field_9-container\" class=\"wpforms-field wpforms-field-radio\" data-field-id=\"9\"><label class=\"wpforms-field-label\">Would you recommend Ditch Assist to other farmers in your area? <span class=\"wpforms-required-label\">*<\/span><\/label><ul id=\"wpforms-209409-field_9\" class=\"wpforms-field-required\"><li class=\"choice-1 depth-1\"><input type=\"radio\" id=\"wpforms-209409-field_9_1\" name=\"wpforms[fields][9]\" value=\"Yes\" required ><label class=\"wpforms-field-label-inline\" for=\"wpforms-209409-field_9_1\">Yes<\/label><\/li><li class=\"choice-2 depth-1\"><input type=\"radio\" id=\"wpforms-209409-field_9_2\" name=\"wpforms[fields][9]\" value=\"No\" required ><label class=\"wpforms-field-label-inline\" for=\"wpforms-209409-field_9_2\">No<\/label><\/li><li class=\"choice-3 depth-1\"><input type=\"radio\" id=\"wpforms-209409-field_9_3\" name=\"wpforms[fields][9]\" value=\"Maybe\" required ><label class=\"wpforms-field-label-inline\" for=\"wpforms-209409-field_9_3\">Maybe<\/label><\/li><\/ul><\/div><div id=\"wpforms-209409-field_11-container\" class=\"wpforms-field wpforms-field-textarea\" data-field-id=\"11\"><label class=\"wpforms-field-label\" for=\"wpforms-209409-field_11\">Kindly share your reasons for your selection above and offer any additional feedback on Ditch Assist <span class=\"wpforms-required-label\">*<\/span><\/label><textarea id=\"wpforms-209409-field_11\" class=\"wpforms-field-medium wpforms-field-required\" name=\"wpforms[fields][11]\" required><\/textarea><div class=\"wpforms-field-description\">We may not be able to fulfill every request but we do value your feedback, which greatly influences future Ditch Assist updates and features.<\/div><\/div><div id=\"wpforms-209409-field_13-container\" class=\"wpforms-field wpforms-field-checkbox\" data-field-id=\"13\"><label class=\"wpforms-field-label\">Disclaimer &amp; End User License <span class=\"wpforms-required-label\">*<\/span><\/label><ul id=\"wpforms-209409-field_13\" class=\"wpforms-field-required\"><li class=\"choice-1 depth-1\"><input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"wpforms-209409-field_13_1\" name=\"wpforms[fields][13][]\" value=\"I acknowledge and agree to the following:\" required ><label class=\"wpforms-field-label-inline\" for=\"wpforms-209409-field_13_1\">I acknowledge and agree to the following:<\/label><\/li><\/ul><div class=\"wpforms-field-description\">1. The data is provided \"as-is\" without warranties, guarantees, or representations of any kind, either express or implied. <br>\r\n2. The user assumes full responsibility for any decisions made based on this data.\r\nNorthern Plains Drainage Systems and any associated persons or entities accept no liability or responsibility for any errors, omissions, or inaccuracies in the data, or for any loss or damage arising from its use.<br>\r\n3. Uninterrupted access to the data portal is not guaranteed and may be affected by factors beyond our control.<br>\r\n4. Free access to the portal for Ditch Assist owners is granted for a 12-month period only. Beyond this period, we reserve the right to continue, terminate, or charge for access at our sole discretion.<br>\r\n5. Users with complementary access may use data exclusively for lands they own or farm. Data concerning lands not owned by the user cannot be sold, shared, or given to third parties, even as screenshots, whether for free or payment. We actively monitor usage and social media for violations. Breaches will prompt action to protect our intellectual property rights.<\/div><\/div><\/div><!-- .wpforms-field-container --><div class=\"wpforms-recaptcha-container wpforms-is-recaptcha wpforms-is-recaptcha-type-v3\" ><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"wpforms[recaptcha]\" value=\"\"><\/div><div class=\"wpforms-submit-container\" ><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"wpforms[id]\" value=\"209409\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"page_title\" value=\"\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"page_url\" value=\"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/209377\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"url_referer\" value=\"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/idm\/\"><button type=\"submit\" name=\"wpforms[submit]\" id=\"wpforms-submit-209409\" class=\"wpforms-submit\" data-alt-text=\"Sending...\" data-submit-text=\"Submit\" aria-live=\"assertive\" value=\"wpforms-submit\">Submit<\/button><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/wp-content\/plugins\/wpforms-lite\/assets\/images\/submit-spin.svg\" class=\"wpforms-submit-spinner\" style=\"display: none;\" width=\"26\" height=\"26\" alt=\"Loading\"><\/div><\/form><\/div>  <!-- .wpforms-container -->\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"et_pb_row_11 et_pb_row et_flex_row\"><div class=\"et_pb_column_21 et_pb_column et-last-child et_flex_column et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et_flex_column_24_24 et_flex_column_24_24_tablet et_flex_column_24_24_phone\"><div class=\"et_pb_text_20 et_pb_text et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_module et_flex_module\"><div class=\"et_pb_text_inner\"><h3><strong>Data Privacy Notice:<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p><strong>We value and respect your privacy.<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><strong>Data Collection<\/strong>: When you sign up, we collect personal data such as your name, email address, and other relevant details. This information is crucial for providing you with access to our portal and tailoring our services to your needs.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Purpose<\/strong>: We use this data solely for the purpose of providing, enhancing, and personalising your experience on our portal. We do not sell, rent, or share your personal information with third parties for their marketing purposes.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Data Protection<\/strong>: We implement robust security measures to ensure that your data is protected from unauthorized access, loss, misuse, or alteration.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Your Rights<\/strong>: You have the right to request access to, modification of, or deletion of your personal data held by us. Should you wish to exercise any of these rights or have any questions regarding your data, please contact our support team.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Changes to this Notice<\/strong>: We may update this privacy notice from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or for other operational, legal, or regulatory reasons. We recommend reviewing it regularly.<\/p>\n<p>By signing up and using our portal, you acknowledge and agree to our data processing as described in this notice.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"et_pb_section_3 et_pb_section et_section_regular et_flex_section\"><div class=\"et_pb_row_12 et_pb_row et_flex_row\"><div class=\"et_pb_column_22 et_pb_column et-last-child et_flex_column et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et_flex_column_24_24 et_flex_column_24_24_tablet et_flex_column_24_24_phone\"><div class=\"et_pb_text_21 et_pb_text et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_module et_flex_module preset--module--divi-text--5c12ac9f-ce18-4be0-9b45-2e257c1c222a\"><div class=\"et_pb_text_inner\"><h2>How to Get Started<\/h2>\n<\/div><\/div><div class=\"et_pb_text_22 et_pb_text et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_module et_flex_module preset--module--divi-text--768a51a2-8b3b-49d9-9c45-80abc614d131\"><div class=\"et_pb_text_inner\"><p>You'll receive two emails once we've verified you as a system owner. One will be from us and contains credentials and instructions for downloading IDM and contour map layers directly into your Ditch Assist App. The second will be from <em>The Mango Team<\/em> (our Portal service provider) with a link to complete your signup for Portal access. Sometimes one or both get filtered to Junk\/Spam folders, so please keep an eye out.\u00a0\u00a0<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><div class=\"et_pb_text_23 et_pb_text et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_module et_flex_module preset--module--divi-text--5c12ac9f-ce18-4be0-9b45-2e257c1c222a\"><div class=\"et_pb_text_inner\"><h2>1. Complete Your Portal Signup<\/h2>\n<\/div><\/div><div class=\"et_pb_text_24 et_pb_text et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_module et_flex_module preset--module--divi-text--768a51a2-8b3b-49d9-9c45-80abc614d131\"><div class=\"et_pb_text_inner\"><p>Click the link in the email to Accept the Invitation and set a password you will remember - you'll need this to access the map portal!<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/set_pw-262x300.jpg\" width=\"262\" height=\"300\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-209416 alignnone size-medium\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/set_pw-262x300.jpg 262w, https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/set_pw.jpg 467w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 262px) 100vw, 262px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>In future, navigate to <a href=\"https:\/\/mangomap.com\/npds\/sign-in\">https:\/\/mangomap.com\/npds\/sign-in<\/a> and sign in with your email and password<\/p>\n<p>Open the Map Portal(s) you have access to from here<br \/><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/open-portal-300x177.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"177\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-209417 alignnone size-medium\" \/><\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><div class=\"et_pb_text_25 et_pb_text et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_module et_flex_module preset--module--divi-text--5c12ac9f-ce18-4be0-9b45-2e257c1c222a\"><div class=\"et_pb_text_inner\"><h2>2. View Detailed Elevation &amp; Drainage Info for your Fields via the Portal on your PC, iPad, or Mac<\/h2>\n<\/div><\/div><div class=\"et_pb_text_26 et_pb_text et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_module et_flex_module preset--module--divi-text--768a51a2-8b3b-49d9-9c45-80abc614d131\"><div class=\"et_pb_text_inner\"><p>Zoom and pan or use the Search tool to search by land location to locate your field(s).<br \/><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/search-300x238.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"238\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-209418 alignnone size-medium\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/search-300x238.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/search.jpg 346w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Analyze information, create customized prints or PDF map views, and create + print custom sketches (ideal for documenting proposals for permitting). Accessing the Portal on a mobile device (iPhone or Android) you can also use geolocation to see your location on the map - just be sure to run Google Maps or similar in the background to force the GPS to stay on rather than using cell towers for location!<\/p>\n<p><img data-dominant-color=\"616651\" data-has-transparency=\"false\" style=\"--dominant-color: #616651;\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/Print-Custom-Maps-300x216.webp\" width=\"300\" height=\"216\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-211206 alignnone size-medium not-transparent\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/Print-Custom-Maps-300x216.webp 300w, https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/Print-Custom-Maps-1024x738.webp 1024w, https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/Print-Custom-Maps-768x554.webp 768w, https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/Print-Custom-Maps-1080x779.webp 1080w, https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/Print-Custom-Maps-980x707.webp 980w, https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/Print-Custom-Maps-480x346.webp 480w, https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/Print-Custom-Maps-jpg.webp 1158w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/><\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><div class=\"et_pb_text_27 et_pb_text et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_module et_flex_module preset--module--divi-text--5c12ac9f-ce18-4be0-9b45-2e257c1c222a\"><div class=\"et_pb_text_inner\"><h2>3. Download Data into Ditch Assist<\/h2>\n<\/div><\/div><div class=\"et_pb_text_28 et_pb_text et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_module et_flex_module\"><div class=\"et_pb_text_inner\"><p>You\u2019ll receive detailed email instructions with a URL to link the Ditch Assist App to IDM and contour data. With your tablet connected to the internet, just zoom and pan around your fields to download and cache the map layers. When you're in the field, easily recall the saved maps for accurate, real-time guidance.<\/p>\n<p><img data-dominant-color=\"616250\" data-has-transparency=\"false\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/IDM-and-Contour-Mapping-now-available-in-the-Ditch-Assist-App-300x168.webp\" width=\"300\" height=\"168\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-211207 alignnone size-medium not-transparent\" style=\"--dominant-color: #616250; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/IDM-and-Contour-Mapping-now-available-in-the-Ditch-Assist-App-300x168.webp 300w, https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/IDM-and-Contour-Mapping-now-available-in-the-Ditch-Assist-App-768x430.webp 768w, https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/IDM-and-Contour-Mapping-now-available-in-the-Ditch-Assist-App-480x269.webp 480w, https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/IDM-and-Contour-Mapping-now-available-in-the-Ditch-Assist-App-jpg.webp 873w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/><\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"et_pb_section_4 et_pb_section et_section_regular et_flex_section\"><\/div>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-209377","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/209377","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=209377"}],"version-history":[{"count":11,"href":"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/209377\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":213156,"href":"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/209377\/revisions\/213156"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.ditchassist.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=209377"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}